Don‚Äôt
- Don‚Äôt inject secrets into `frontend/index.html`
- Don‚Äôt rely on `process.env` in browser JavaScript
- Don‚Äôt ship changes without verifying `npm run test` and a clean report
- Don't commit `node_modules/`

